sub_title: Owner & Cellular Healing Practitioner at Healing Transformations
summary:
Ellen Hol is the founder and owner of Healing Transformations Pte Ltd where she has worked as a practitioner in mind-body and cellular healing in her private practice in Singapore and Thailand since 2003 to help people heal and transform their lives and open into their boundless potential. Ellen works with people facing the myriad of emotional and physical issues as well as to prevent dis-ease.  

Her mission is to transform people’s lives by guiding them to let go of their emotional pain, reinvent their Self to initiate New Beginnings, Self-Realization and Spiritual Awakening and to live their life with passion, meaning and purpose. 

Ellen is the creator of Healing Transformations therapy, a cutting-edge therapy and one of the most powerful healing processes available today where healing takes place at cellular level. Healing Transformations therapy combines aspects of meditation, regression therapy, hypnotherapy and deep emotional release techniques with NLP, psycho-therapeutic tools and forgiveness from the level of the soul blended with Ellen’s personal touch and intuitive skills based on more than 15 years of experience in her field. 

She also designed the Total Transformation Program, an in-depth and integrated holistic health program that addresses all essential aspects of emotional, mental, physical and spiritual health.

With her life transforming therapies, Ellen has helped thousands of people throughout the world to successfully transform their lives to higher levels, becoming the best they can be.

Formerly, Ellen worked as a bereavement counselor in Dover Park Hospice and the CDC in Singapore where she counseled people with terminal cancer, HIV and AIDS and their family members on a voluntary basis during 4 years. 

Ellen has been trained by the best in the field of mind-body healing, personal transformation and is a passionate life-long learner.

Ellen's greatest passion is to be a Force for Good and to create real change in the lives of others.

Specialties: Mind-Body therapies and personal growth work with a holistic approach to heal and completely let go of emotional and (sometimes) physical issues at cellular level. 

Guide people to Open Into Their Boundless Potential and Become The Best They Can Be.

Healing Transformations Therapy is available for adults, teens and children from 5 years old.

I felt grateful for being able to help our patients come to terms with their death and deal with their unfinished business. Yet another part of me felt frustrated that they all died, because I knew that if the patients would have had access to alternative therapies at an earlier stage in their lives and let go of their psychological and emotional pain, at least some of them would have survived.”
